  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "source": [
    "UDP is working on one way traffic and it doesnt need the connection of the other side.\n",
    "TCP is balanced connection that send and recieve data for both sides so the average is moch lower.\n"
   ],
   "id": "74b97b74c6f7295b"
  },
  {
